Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,town_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:04.64,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君の手紙を読んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:08.84,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,終わったはずの午後に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.92,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,それが全部嘘だと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:16.04,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕にはわかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:19.45,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しいときでさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:23.15,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,笑ってしまう君を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.82,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,守ると言った言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.96,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘にはしたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.73,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,アイツらだって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.84,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってくれるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.81,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:47.08,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君のいる町
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:51.66,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな答えが待っていても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:55.04,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,構わないから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.86,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,そこへ行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:02.01,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君のいる町
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:04.92,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君の心が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:09.46,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕を呼んでいるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:14.02,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:17.00,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君のいる町
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.68,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君の心が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:24.32,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕を呼んでいるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:28.28,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,聞こえるから
